    "body": "Pressing Ctrl-C while cythonizing doesn't work and leaves you with a hung compilation that continues to catch !KeyboardInterrupt. Annoying, especially in Sage where the compilation can take a long time. The well-known problem is that `Pool.map` doesn't play nice with !KeyboardInterrupt\n\nAt 2014-04-09T18:05:54Z **vbraun** added attachment [cythonize_keyboardinterrupt.patch](https://gist.github.com/d899611318074890eb5963ba482007d2)\n\nMigrated from http://trac.cython.org/ticket/827",
